N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 160.38 - Compliance with other laws

State Regulations

In the course of its operation of an appearance enhancement
business, an owner shall refrain from engaging in any conduct violative of any

State or Federal law, rule or regulation. Notes
